Isabel Maria Adrian (born 30 August 1977 in Gothenburg) is a Swedish television personality, producer and author. She was a contestant in Expedition Robinson 2004 which was broadcast on TV3 and also made a centerfold in the men's magazine Caf√© the same year. Adrian has worked as a model, is a well-known Swedish and international blogger since many years back and a clothing designer. In 2013 she married the DJ Steve Angello who is one third of the legendary music group Swedish House Mafia. Adrian and Angello reside in Los Angeles and the couple have now two daughters together, Monday Lily (6) and Winter Rose (4).
